        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We're thrilled to announce the launch of Tilley Sport's newest golf apparel collection, now available at TrendyGolf. Known for their legacy of innovation in headwear, Tilley Sport has expanded their expertise into a full range of golf apparel, blending high-performance functionality with sophisticated style.</p>"
