        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Tilley Sport stands out by merging sport and sophistication. Their latest collection continues this tradition, offering modern designs that transition effortlessly from the golf course to everyday life. By focusing on detail and innovation, Tilley Sport provides apparel that enhances your performance while reflecting your style.</p><p>Explore Tilley Sport's new collection at TrendyGolf and elevate your game with apparel that meets the highest standards of both function and fashion.</p>"
